OL,3,CMajor lithium mining investment could
OL,4,Ccreate 'thousands of jobs' for Cornwall
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on Cornwall's
OL,7,Fgrowing minerals industry
OL,9,FThe Government is promising to invest
OL,10,Fup to #50million to boost production
OL,11,Fat Cornwall's lithium and tungsten
OL,12,Fmines - and it could mean thousands of
OL,13,Fnew jobs for the county.
