OL,3,CMajor lithium mining investment could
OL,4,Ccreate 'thousands of jobs' for Cornwall
OL,6,FOn Tuesday Chris McDonald, Labour's
OL,7,Findustry minister, visited Camborne
OL,8,FSchool of Mines and Cornish Lithium
OL,9,Fnear St Austell to unveil the new
OL,10,Fstrategy, saying Cornwall's natural
OL,11,Fresources will play a big part in its
OL,12,Fplan to meet ten percent of mineral
OL,13,Fdemand through domestic production.
OL,15,F"Demand for critical minerals,
OL,16,Fincluding in the UK, is increasing all
OL,17,Fof the time," Mr McDonald said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
