OL,3,CMajor lithium mining investment could
OL,4,Ccreate 'thousands of jobs' for Cornwall
OL,6,F"So somehow we need to increase
OL,7,Fsupply. But at the moment the
OL,8,Fprocessing of the minerals is very
OL,9,Fmuch dominated by a single country, by
OL,10,FChina.
OL,12,F"In some areas they are between 70 and
OL,13,F90% of the processing. And it's never
OL,14,Fa good idea if there's only one shop
OL,15,Fyou can go to to buy things.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
