OL,3,CMajor lithium mining investment could
OL,4,Ccreate 'thousands of jobs' for Cornwall
OL,6,F"I recognise the fundamental, crucial
OL,7,Fimportance of Cornwall to delivering
OL,8,Fthis strategy, and the world leading
OL,9,Fdeposits of minerals and the rich
OL,10,Fheritage and skills that there are in
OL,11,FCornwall for mining and processing."
OL,13,FThe Government says it wants to be
OL,14,Fproducing at least 50,000 tonnes of
OL,15,Flithium in the UK by 2035.
OL,17,FIt wants ten per cent of the UK's
OL,18,Ftotal mineral needs to be homegrown,
OL,19,Fand is offering up to #50million in
OL,20,Fnew funding to make it all happen.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
