OL,3,CMajor lithium mining investment could
OL,4,Ccreate 'thousands of jobs' for Cornwall
OL,6,FPerran Moon, Labour MP for Camborne,
OL,7,FRedruth and Hayle, said: "This is
OL,8,Fgoing to create thousands of jobs in
OL,9,Fmining and in the supply chain over
OL,10,Fthe next few years.
OL,12,F"We're seeing our young people really
OL,13,Fengaging, both in terms of geology,
OL,14,Fbut also in roles like construction
OL,15,Fand engineering and electricals.
OL,17,F"These are really, really important
OL,18,Fjobs, and the sector knows that we
OL,19,Fmust focus and invest in our young
OL,20,Fpeople in order to make this happen. "
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
