OL,3,CMajor lithium mining investment could
OL,4,Ccreate 'thousands of jobs' for Cornwall
OL,6,FThe Minister rounded off his day with
OL,7,Fa visit to the lab at Cornish Lithium
OL,8,Fnear St Austell, one of the companies
OL,9,Fat the forefront of the county's
OL,10,Fmodern mineral revolution.
OL,12,FCornish Lithium CEO Jeremy Wrathall
OL,13,Fsaid: "I see it as a big vote of
OL,14,Fconfidence for Cornwall. The fact they
OL,15,Frecognise that these critical minerals
OL,16,Fhave to come from Cornwall.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
